521            }
522        }

525        if (isset($classAttributes[Mapping\AttributeOverrides::class])) {

539        // Evaluate EntityListeners attribute
540        if (isset($classAttributes[Mapping\EntityListeners::class])) {

572        }

575        if (isset($classAttributes[Mapping\HasLifecycleCallbacks::class])) {

578            }

646                $callbacks[] = [$method->name, Events::postUpdate];
647            }

728            'precision' => $column->precision,

733        }
734
735        if (isset($column->name)) {
736            $mapping['columnName'] = $column->name;
737        }
738
739        if (isset($column->columnDefinition)) {
